      <title>沙特阿拉伯提高对亚洲石油价格，表明对需求有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/saudi-arabia-hikes-oil-prices-to-asia-in-sign-of-faith-in-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯三个月来首次上调了对亚洲出口的旗舰原油价格，这一初步迹象表明，沙特阿拉伯对全球最大进口国亚洲的需求仍有信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/saudi-arabia-hikes-oil-prices-to-asia-in-sign-of-faith-in-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:50:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
